---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HeartStrings Play - A Premium Social Board Game"
  description="HeartStrings Play is the first public launch product from ByteLite LLC. A premium social board game for couples, dates, and intimate gatherings. Guided by AIya and AIon. Six escalating card tiers."
  keywords={["HeartStrings Play", "social board game", "relationship game", "couples game", "AIya", "AIon", "HeartStrings", "ByteLite LLC"]}
  schemaType="Product"
>

  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <img
      src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-gameboard.png"
      alt="HeartStrings Play - premium social board game"
      width="900"
      height="900"
      class="hero-board-img"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="launch-pill">Launch Product</span>
        <h1>HeartStrings Play</h1>
        <p class="hero-tagline">A premium social board game. Guided by AIya and AIon.<br/>Built for couples, dates, and intimate gatherings.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-pink">Express Interest</a>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="btn btn-rose-outline">See the App Companion</a>
          <a href="/status" class="btn btn-outline">Current Status</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What is the Game -->
  <section class="game-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-copy">
          <h2>What is HeartStrings Play?</h2>
          <p>HeartStrings Play is a premium social board game designed to create genuine connection and chemistry between players. It is not a generic trivia night. It is not a one-trick dare deck. It is a structured, guided experience that escalates naturally through six card tiers.</p>
          <p>Two to four players navigate the heart-shaped board, drawing cards that open conversation, build vulnerability, and raise the stakes at a pace the players control. AIya and AIon serve as your session hosts -- appearing on the board and in the companion app to guide, prompt, and respond.</p>
          <div class="intro-specs">
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Players</span>
              <span class="spec-value">2 -- 4</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Session Length</span>
              <span class="spec-value">45 -- 90 min</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Card Tiers</span>
              <span class="spec-value">6</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec-item">
              <span class="spec-label">Audience</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Adults</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-visual">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-decree-card.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Decree card"
            width="280"
            height="400"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="decree-card-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Plays -->
  <section class="how-it-plays">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>How It Plays</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Six escalating card tiers. One heart-shaped board. You set the pace.</p>

      <div class="tier-grid">
        <div class="tier-card tier-1">
          <div class="tier-number">01</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Initiate</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Opening moves. Light questions that reveal personality, values, and style without pressure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-2">
          <div class="tier-number">02</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Connect</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Deeper conversation. Stories, preferences, and discoveries that build real familiarity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-3">
          <div class="tier-number">03</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Seduce</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Flirtatious tension. Prompts that invite playfulness and signal mutual attraction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-4">
          <div class="tier-number">04</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Stimulate</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Bold territory. Honest answers, revealing moments, deliberate provocation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-5">
          <div class="tier-number">05</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Edge</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">High-stakes prompts for players who want to push the experience further.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-card tier-6">
          <div class="tier-number">06</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Climax</div>
          <p class="tier-desc">Peak experience. The final tier is earned, not jumped to. What happens is between the players.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Different -->
  <section class="why-different">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="diff-inner">
        <h2>Not Like Other Games</h2>
        <div class="diff-grid">
          <div class="diff-col bad">
            <div class="diff-label bad">Generic alternatives</div>
            <ul class="diff-list">
              <li>Random dare decks with no progression</li>
              <li>Trivia nights that avoid intimacy entirely</li>
              <li>Party games that peak in the first ten minutes</li>
              <li>No guided host or framing</li>
              <li>No connection to any digital layer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="diff-col good">
            <div class="diff-label good">HeartStrings Play</div>
            <ul class="diff-list">
              <li>Six tiers that escalate at your pace</li>
              <li>AIya and AIon as in-session guides</li>
              <li>Premium materials designed for repeat play</li>
              <li>Structured progression, not random chaos</li>
              <li>Connects to the HeartStrings App ecosystem</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AIya + AIon Guide Section -->
  <section class="guides-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guides-inner">
        <div class="guides-copy">
          <h2>Meet AIya and AIon</h2>
          <p>AIya and AIon are the AI guides designed for the HeartStrings world. On the board they appear as hosts. In the HeartStrings App they become interactive -- responding, suggesting, and helping players understand their compatibility.</p>
          <p>They are not just mascots. They are the connective tissue between the physical game and the digital companion layer.</p>
          <ul class="guide-features">
            <li>Host and frame each session</li>
            <li>Appear on the board and in the companion app</li>
            <li>Guide players through the tier progression</li>
            <li>Power the compatibility and matching layer in the app</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="btn btn-rose-outline" style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:inline-block;">See them in the App</a>
        </div>
        <div class="guides-visual">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-guides-banner.png"
            alt="AIya and AIon - HeartStrings AI guides"
            width="480"
            height="320"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="guides-banner-img"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <section class="gallery-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Game Gallery</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Board design, character guides, and game components.</p>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-item gallery-large">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-gameboard.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Play game board"
            width="600"
            height="600"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Game Board -- Heart-shaped path with 40 spaces</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-aion-portrait.png"
            alt="AIon game character portrait"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">AIon -- Session guide</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-aiya-portrait.png"
            alt="AIya game character portrait"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">AIya -- Session guide</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-decree-card.png"
            alt="HeartStrings Decree card"
            width="280"
            height="400"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Decree card design</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-tokens-1.png"
            alt="Game tokens"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Game tokens (set 1)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-tokens-2.png"
            alt="Game tokens"
            width="280"
            height="280"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="gallery-caption">Game tokens (set 2)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Honest Status -->
  <section class="honesty-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="honesty-inner">
        <h2>Where Things Stand</h2>
        <div class="honesty-grid">
          <div class="honesty-card live">
            <div class="honesty-label live">Done</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Game board design (final)</li>
              <li>Card deck tier structure (6 tiers)</li>
              <li>AIya and AIon character design</li>
              <li>Token set design</li>
              <li>Game rules and mechanics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="honesty-card indev">
            <div class="honesty-label indev">In Development</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Physical prototype production</li>
              <li>Card deck print run</li>
              <li>Manufacturing specifications</li>
              <li>Packaging design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="honesty-card planned">
            <div class="honesty-label planned">Planned</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Manufacturing partner selected</li>
              <li>Retail / direct launch</li>
              <li>HeartStrings App integration</li>
              <li>Expanded card expansions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Waitlist CTA -->
  <section class="waitlist-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="waitlist-inner">
        <h2>Be First to Know</h2>
        <p>HeartStrings Play is in active development. Express interest now and we will contact you directly when the game is available for purchase or pre-order.</p>
        <div class="waitlist-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-pink">Express Interest</a>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-outline">Subscribe for Updates</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bridge to App -->
  <section class="bridge-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bridge-inner">
        <div class="bridge-copy">
          <span class="bridge-eyebrow">The Companion Layer</span>
          <h2>HeartStrings App</h2>
          <p>Play creates the shared language. The app extends it -- profiles, guided matching, compatibility rationale, and AIya and AIon as digital guides who already know how your session went.</p>
          <p>The app is currently in development. The UI design exists. The matching engine is being built on ByteLite infrastructure.</p>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="btn btn-rose-outline" style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:inline-block;">See the HeartStrings App</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bridge-visual">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-app-logo.png"
            alt="HeartStrings App"
            width="200"
            height="200"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="bridge-app-logo"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero-banner {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #0A0E27;
    min-height: 420px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-board-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    opacity: 0.22;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .launch-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.2);
    color: #EC4899;
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-overlay h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #EC4899 60%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 1.5vw, 1.0625rem);
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.85);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .btn-pink {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EC4899 0%, #BE185D 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-pink:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4); }

  .btn-rose-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #FB7185;
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.4);
  }
  .btn-rose-outline:hover {
    border-color: #FB7185;
    background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5);
    color: #E0E0E0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Game Intro */
  .game-intro {
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #EC4899;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .intro-copy p {
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.75);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .intro-specs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .spec-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4);
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #EC4899;
  }

  .decree-card-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.25);
  }

  /* How It Plays */
  .how-it-plays {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060813 0%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.03) 50%, #060813 100%);
  }

  .how-it-plays h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .tier-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tier-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .tier-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .tier-number {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }

  .tier-name {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .tier-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tier-1 { border: 1px solid rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.3); }
  .tier-1 .tier-name { color: #FFB6C1; }
  .tier-2 { border: 1px solid rgba(255, 105, 135, 0.3); }
  .tier-2 .tier-name { color: #FF6987; }
  .tier-3 { border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4); }
  .tier-3 .tier-name { color: #EC4899; }
  .tier-4 { border: 1px solid rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.4); }
  .tier-4 .tier-name { color: #DB2777; }
  .tier-5 { border: 1px solid rgba(190, 24, 93, 0.4); }
  .tier-5 .tier-name { color: #BE185D; }
  .tier-6 { border: 1px solid rgba(157, 23, 77, 0.5); }
  .tier-6 .tier-name { color: #9D174D; }
  .tier-6:hover { box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(157, 23, 77, 0.2); }

  /* Why Different */
  .why-different {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .diff-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .diff-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .diff-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .diff-col {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .diff-col.bad {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .diff-col.good {
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.25);
  }

  .diff-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .diff-label.bad { color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.35); }
  .diff-label.good { color: #EC4899; }

  .diff-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .diff-list li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
  }

  .diff-col.bad .diff-list li::before {
    content: '--';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.2);
  }

  .diff-col.good .diff-list li::before {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #EC4899;
  }

  /* Guides Section */
  .guides-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060813 0%, rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.04) 50%, #060813 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1);
  }

  .guides-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .guides-copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .guides-copy p {
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.75);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .guide-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .guide-features li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .guide-features li::before {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #FB7185;
  }

  .guides-banner-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.15);
  }

  /* Gallery */
  .gallery-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .gallery-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .gallery-item {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .gallery-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.25);
  }

  .gallery-large {
    grid-column: 1;
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
  }

  .gallery-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .gallery-large img {
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.4);
  }

  .gallery-caption {
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Honesty Section */
  .honesty-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060813 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.02) 50%, #060813 100%);
  }

  .honesty-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
